        <name>GetRoll</name>
        <qualifiedname>Dali::TiltSensor::GetRoll</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Query the roll value. This is in the range -1 to 1. When the device is lying face-up on a flat surface, this method will return a value close to zero. A value close to 1 indicates that the right-side of the device is pointing upwards. A value close to -1 indicates that the right-side of the device is pointing downwards. <simplesect kind="pre"><para>The tilt-sensor is started. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The roll value. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
